290
00:15:44,910 --> 00:15:46,040
I've figured it out.

291
00:15:47,390 --> 00:15:47,870
What...

292
00:15:48,510 --> 00:15:49,570
what are you doing?

293
00:15:51,390 --> 00:15:52,390
Did you hear that?

294
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:54,030
You said something?

295
00:15:54,030 --> 00:15:55,290
I didn't say anything.

296
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:57,380
It just went "crack." Did you hear it?

297
00:15:57,910 --> 00:15:58,630
This is bad...

298
00:15:58,630 --> 00:15:59,690
this is really bad.

299
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:01,770
I didn't hear anything.

300
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,360
It's fine. What were you saying?

301
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:07,200
Before Captain Ye

302
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:08,150
was killed,

303
00:16:08,240 --> 00:16:09,970
why did he write down your name?

304
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:12,120
Even when

305
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:14,720
someone knows they're about to die,

306
00:16:15,270 --> 00:16:17,330
they instinctively call for help...

307
00:16:17,670 --> 00:16:19,420
or try to stop the bleeding.

308
00:16:19,750 --> 00:16:21,280
But Captain Ye did neither.

309
00:16:21,400 --> 00:16:22,900
In his final moment,

310
00:16:24,150 --> 00:16:25,550
he still wrote your name.

311
00:16:26,750 --> 00:16:27,320
Why?

312
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:30,270
Why?

313
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:32,200
You must have

314
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:34,800
uncovered a key lead
in Chief Lu's murder case.

315
00:16:35,150 --> 00:16:36,530
Maybe you didn't even realize it—

316
00:16:36,530 --> 00:16:38,270
but there was definitely something.

317
00:16:38,270 --> 00:16:39,730
Captain Ye noticed it too,

318
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:42,180
and he was silenced because of it.

319
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:44,150
He wrote your name

320
00:16:45,630 --> 00:16:46,630
because you're the only one

321
00:16:46,630 --> 00:16:47,960
who can solve this case.

322
00:16:48,150 --> 00:16:48,670
Chief.

323
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:52,240
Right now... I'm afraid my hands are tied.

324
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:52,910
Why?

325
00:16:53,790 --> 00:16:54,750
Just a second

326
00:16:54,790 --> 00:16:55,850
before you came in,

327
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:57,790
this injured spot

328
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:58,970
got hit badly again.

329
00:17:00,150 --> 00:17:00,750
I told you,

330
00:17:00,750 --> 00:17:02,480
the hospitals here aren't reliable.

331
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:04,510
Then let's try another hospital.

332
00:17:05,349 --> 00:17:06,069
Li Qian,

333
00:17:07,069 --> 00:17:07,829
it looks like you're going to

334
00:17:07,829 --> 00:17:09,290
have to handle this alone.

335
00:17:12,849 --> 00:17:17,160
[Sanjiangkou Evening News]

336
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:14,640
Time to eat. Let's go.

337
00:17:14,859 --> 00:17:15,750
Finally, I'm off work.

338
00:17:15,750 --> 00:17:17,030
I'm exhausted—it's been a long morning.

339
00:17:17,030 --> 00:17:18,550
What did you eat earlier today?

340
00:17:18,550 --> 00:17:19,069
I'm starving.

341
00:17:19,069 --> 00:17:20,720
I'll grab a bowl of noodles first.

342
00:17:20,720 --> 00:17:21,310
Eat more.

343
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:23,440
There's still work this afternoon.

344
00:17:27,950 --> 00:17:34,750
[Sanjiangkou Evening News]

345
00:17:28,109 --> 00:17:28,690
Sir,

346
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:30,320
we left a power drill behind.

347
00:17:30,510 --> 00:17:31,480
A power drill?

348
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:34,650
Come with me.

349
00:17:41,750 --> 00:17:44,810
[7th Floor – News Department]

350
00:17:53,630 --> 00:17:56,110
♪ Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny,
bunny, bunny ♪

351
00:17:53,750 --> 00:18:01,630
[News Department]

352
00:17:57,140 --> 00:17:58,400
♪ Love you, love you, love you ♪

353
00:17:59,890 --> 00:18:02,300
♪ Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny,
bunny, bunny ♪

354
00:18:03,180 --> 00:18:04,620
♪ Love you, love you, love you ♪

355
00:18:05,730 --> 00:18:06,540
♪ Oh Gimme ♪

356
00:18:07,760 --> 00:18:09,600
♪ Dance me in the richness ♪

357
00:18:10,770 --> 00:18:12,290
♪ Raining make it rain ♪

358
00:18:12,830 --> 00:18:15,550
♪ Oh cash is my revolution ♪

359
00:18:25,630 --> 00:18:27,290
Everything's under control.

360
00:18:27,640 --> 00:18:28,300
Get to work.

361
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:31,620
What kind of work are we doing?

362
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:34,080
Roach control.

363
00:18:36,750 --> 00:18:37,640
Roach control?

364
00:18:38,510 --> 00:18:40,160
I didn't hear anything about that.

365
00:18:40,160 --> 00:18:40,890
Let me check.

366
00:18:47,860 --> 00:18:49,120
Let me do it. I'll do it.

367
00:19:06,710 --> 00:19:08,500
Do you have Plan B?

368
00:19:08,720 --> 00:19:10,250
Plan B in your dream.

369
00:19:10,820 --> 00:19:12,880
Hello, is this the Logistics office?

370
00:19:14,270 --> 00:19:14,830
I'm just checking—

371
00:19:14,830 --> 00:19:16,830
did we schedule anyone to come over—

372
00:19:19,060 --> 00:19:20,320
It's here! Here! Here!

373
00:19:21,310 --> 00:19:22,040
A cockroach!

374
00:19:22,110 --> 00:19:23,000
Move! Move!

375
00:19:29,790 --> 00:19:30,680
Keep watch outside.

376
00:19:30,680 --> 00:19:31,330
They'll be back

377
00:19:31,330 --> 00:19:32,330
from lunch at 1 PM.

378
00:19:32,630 --> 00:19:34,430
I'll try my best to do it quickly.

379
00:19:35,930 --> 00:19:36,990
What are you doing?

380
00:19:37,270 --> 00:19:37,960
I just want to know

381
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:39,200
what we're actually here for today.

382
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:40,320
To work.

383
00:19:40,350 --> 00:19:41,750
Go keep watch at the door.

384
00:19:48,460 --> 00:19:50,580
[Sanjiangkou Exclusive Interview
Press Release]

385
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:53,230
[Exclusive Interview Press Release:
Fang Yong]

386
00:19:53,250 --> 00:19:53,680
[My Poetry, My Faraway]

387
00:20:23,830 --> 00:20:25,630
Bro, what exactly are you doing?

388
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:26,940
It's 12:50 PM already.

389
00:20:27,680 --> 00:20:28,480
Almost done.

390
00:20:32,670 --> 00:20:33,830
Hey, why are you staring at me?

391
00:20:33,830 --> 00:20:34,720
Watch the elevator—

392
00:20:34,720 --> 00:20:35,460
tell me if anyone comes.

393
00:20:35,460 --> 00:20:36,240
Alright.

394
00:20:39,410 --> 00:20:42,390
[Copying...]

395
00:20:42,530 --> 00:20:44,750
[From Press Release to Drive E]

396
00:20:56,270 --> 00:20:57,130
Please come in.

397
00:20:58,720 --> 00:20:59,270
Chief Qi,

398
00:20:59,960 --> 00:21:01,960
Chief Zhang wants to speak with you.

399
00:21:02,830 --> 00:21:03,490
Where is he?

400
00:21:08,480 --> 00:21:09,070
Chief Qi.

401
00:21:10,790 --> 00:21:12,000
W-What happened to you?

402
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:12,350
I...

403
00:21:12,350 --> 00:21:13,000
How did this...

404
00:21:13,000 --> 00:21:13,720
You were fine just now—

405
00:21:13,720 --> 00:21:14,920
how did you end up in a wheelchair?

406
00:21:14,920 --> 00:21:15,310
No idea.

407
00:21:15,310 --> 00:21:16,310
It just happened.

408
00:21:16,310 --> 00:21:17,350
I was fine a moment ago—

409
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:19,400
then my leg just gave out, went "crack,"

410
00:21:19,400 --> 00:21:20,530
and now I can't stand

411
00:21:20,590 --> 00:21:21,480
or walk.

412
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:22,980
J-Just look at this...

413
00:21:24,270 --> 00:21:25,200
Chief Qi, I'm still a bit worried

414
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:26,600
about the hospital here.

415
00:21:27,110 --> 00:21:28,920
I think I should go back
to the provincial capital for a check-up.

416
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:29,980
Alright, alright.

417
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:32,080
How long will it take?

418
00:21:33,110 --> 00:21:33,830
Hard to say.

419
00:21:35,750 --> 00:21:37,030
The hospital said yesterday

420
00:21:37,030 --> 00:21:38,430
there were no fractures,

421
00:21:38,550 --> 00:21:39,880
but with how it is now...

422
00:21:39,880 --> 00:21:41,110
I don't know if it's neurological

423
00:21:41,110 --> 00:21:42,440
or something deeper.

424
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:45,170
I need to go back
and get a proper diagnosis first.

425
00:21:45,790 --> 00:21:47,720
Whether it takes a few months or...

426
00:21:47,720 --> 00:21:49,180
It's hard to say right now.

427
00:21:51,720 --> 00:21:52,250
Alright,

428
00:21:53,070 --> 00:21:54,200
health comes first.

429
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:55,000
Health always comes first.

430
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:56,530
Actually, I just want to say

431
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:58,300
I'm sorry.

432
00:21:59,000 --> 00:22:00,000
I haven't been here long,

433
00:22:00,000 --> 00:22:00,830
haven't done much work,

434
00:22:00,830 --> 00:22:02,590
and now I've even gotten injured myself—

435
00:22:02,590 --> 00:22:03,550
sorry for causing trouble.

436
00:22:03,550 --> 00:22:05,080
W-What kind of talk is that?

437
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:06,350
You've done outstanding work.

438
00:22:06,350 --> 00:22:07,310
I'll arrange

439
00:22:07,310 --> 00:22:08,710
a proper farewell dinner

440
00:22:09,000 --> 00:22:10,230
and treat you well.

441
00:22:10,400 --> 00:22:11,200
No need for dinner.

442
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:11,960
I just came

443
00:22:11,960 --> 00:22:12,720
to say goodbye.

444
00:22:12,720 --> 00:22:13,510
I'll head back right away.

445
00:22:13,510 --> 00:22:14,030
No, no,

446
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:16,010
you must attend the dinner.

447
00:22:16,230 --> 00:22:17,490
Tonight after dinner,

448
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:20,040
I'll personally see you off
to the station.

449
00:22:20,270 --> 00:22:21,000
Is that okay?

450
00:22:54,960 --> 00:22:55,480
Sir.

451
00:22:55,790 --> 00:22:56,200
Sir...

452
00:22:57,310 --> 00:22:58,110
What's wrong?

453
00:23:03,720 --> 00:23:04,780
What's the matter?

454
00:23:05,640 --> 00:23:06,960
W-What happened?

455
00:23:07,070 --> 00:23:07,870
I'm dizzy...

456
00:23:08,340 --> 00:23:09,140
Dizzy, dizzy.

457
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:10,220
Low blood sugar?

458
00:23:09,260 --> 00:23:10,510
[Copying...]

459
00:23:11,290 --> 00:23:12,160
I've got candy in my room, hold on—

460
00:23:12,160 --> 00:23:12,760
No, no.

461
00:23:12,790 --> 00:23:13,480
Sir, sir,

462
00:23:14,110 --> 00:23:14,880
I, I... Y-You

463
00:23:14,880 --> 00:23:16,200
just press my Zusanli point.

464
00:23:16,200 --> 00:23:16,640
Press it.

465
00:23:16,640 --> 00:23:17,720
Trust me, my family's been

466
00:23:17,720 --> 00:23:18,880
traditional Chinese doctors
for 6 generations.

467
00:23:18,880 --> 00:23:20,010
Just press Zusanli.

468
00:23:20,320 --> 00:23:21,070
Here, here, here.

469
00:23:21,070 --> 00:23:21,600
Zusanli?

470
00:23:21,650 --> 00:23:22,640
Yes, yes, that's the one.

471
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:23,720
Yes, right here. Here.

472
00:23:23,720 --> 00:23:24,200
That's right.

473
00:23:24,200 --> 00:23:24,590
Better?

474
00:23:24,590 --> 00:23:25,750
Harder... harder...

475
00:23:25,750 --> 00:23:27,610
Still not good—still not good...

476
00:23:28,510 --> 00:23:29,830
Alright, alright.

477
00:23:29,830 --> 00:23:30,510
Better?

478
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:31,510
I'm good now.

479
00:23:31,790 --> 00:23:32,470
Alright.

480
00:23:34,200 --> 00:23:34,590
It's okay now.

481
00:23:34,590 --> 00:23:35,160
Thank you, Sir.

482
00:23:35,160 --> 00:23:36,110
Thank you, Sir.

483
00:23:38,140 --> 00:23:39,620
What a guy...

484
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:45,510
Bro...

485
00:23:47,310 --> 00:23:48,150
hey bro—

486
00:23:48,270 --> 00:23:49,980
what acupoint do you press

487
00:23:50,070 --> 00:23:52,200
for chronic intestinal obstruction?

488
00:23:54,160 --> 00:23:54,890
Did you hear?

489
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:56,200
Chief Zhang is going back
to the provincial capital.

490
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:57,440
Cut it out. Who told you that?

491
00:23:57,440 --> 00:23:58,040
It's true.

492
00:24:03,160 --> 00:24:04,000
Li Qian...

493
00:24:04,970 --> 00:24:05,830
looks like you're going to

494
00:24:05,830 --> 00:24:07,160
be fighting alone here.

495
00:24:08,160 --> 00:24:08,880
Why is Chief Zhang in such a hurry

496
00:24:08,880 --> 00:24:11,140
to return to the Provincial Department?

497
00:24:13,200 --> 00:24:14,510
During yesterday's DUI checkpoint,

498
00:24:14,510 --> 00:24:16,370
all the ideas were actually mine.

499
00:24:16,750 --> 00:24:17,510
If anything went wrong,

500
00:24:17,510 --> 00:24:19,640
the responsibility should fall on me.

501
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:20,350
There are a lot of things

502
00:24:20,350 --> 00:24:21,810
I can't tell you right now.

503
00:24:21,890 --> 00:24:23,290
But what I can tell you is—

504
00:24:24,240 --> 00:24:24,920
you did

505
00:24:24,920 --> 00:24:26,050
nothing wrong.

506
00:24:26,440 --> 00:24:27,770
You actually helped me.

507
00:24:32,960 --> 00:24:34,110
So that's what it is...

508
00:24:34,110 --> 00:24:34,790
I get it now.

509
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:38,790
Chief Qi.

510
00:24:39,440 --> 00:24:40,070
Thank you.

511
00:24:41,960 --> 00:24:43,070
Alright, alright.

512
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:47,130
I heard Chief Zhang is leaving?

513
00:24:47,130 --> 00:24:48,660
Is his injury that serious?

514
00:24:48,920 --> 00:24:49,370
What's going on?

515
00:24:49,370 --> 00:24:50,700
Chief Qi, Captain Wang—

516
00:24:51,070 --> 00:24:52,530
Chief Zhang cannot leave.

517
00:24:53,880 --> 00:24:55,030
Only he can solve Chief Lu

518
00:24:55,030 --> 00:24:56,360
and Captain Ye's cases.

519
00:24:59,240 --> 00:25:00,110
Be clear.

520
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:02,810
About

521
00:25:03,070 --> 00:25:04,310
the DUI operation—

522
00:25:05,070 --> 00:25:06,240
the idea of setting checkpoints

523
00:25:06,240 --> 00:25:07,450
at all intersections

524
00:25:07,920 --> 00:25:09,180
wasn't Chief Zhang's,

525
00:25:09,750 --> 00:25:11,480
it was Song Xing's suggestion.

526
00:25:11,920 --> 00:25:13,200
At first, I thought

527
00:25:13,720 --> 00:25:16,010
Chief Zhang was just covering
for Song Xing,

528
00:25:16,010 --> 00:25:17,590
trying to keep him
from being criticized by Captain Wang.

529
00:25:17,590 --> 00:25:18,450
But I was wrong.

530
00:25:18,590 --> 00:25:19,520
What do you mean?

531
00:25:20,270 --> 00:25:21,590
Captain Wang, think about it.

532
00:25:21,590 --> 00:25:23,640
Chief Zhang has been a police officer
for years—

533
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:24,840
he must know it's rare

534
00:25:24,960 --> 00:25:25,640
to include non-motor vehicles

535
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:27,400
in DUI checks.

536
00:25:28,200 --> 00:25:29,600
So why did he insist on it?

537
00:25:32,350 --> 00:25:33,310
When Li Feng was arrested,

538
00:25:33,310 --> 00:25:34,030
he said:

539
00:25:35,540 --> 00:25:37,270
"Last night I had a bad feeling.

540
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:39,920
You even checked non-motor vehicles

541
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:41,240
during DUI enforcement—

542
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:42,570
were you coming for me?"

543
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:44,110
That's impossible.

544
00:25:44,110 --> 00:25:45,910
What, is he some kind of prophet?

545
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:46,960
Remember

546
00:25:47,160 --> 00:25:48,000
when Chief Zhang was here

547
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:49,030
personally running point

548
00:25:49,030 --> 00:25:50,000
on the DUI crackdown?

549
00:25:50,000 --> 00:25:51,480
He said, "'One mistake: their tears,

550
00:25:51,480 --> 00:25:52,400
your blood.'

551
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:55,300
We've got to take this seriously.

552
00:25:56,800 --> 00:26:00,260
You never know, we might even
stumble onto something bigger."

553
00:26:02,960 --> 00:26:05,560
At Li Feng's house...

554
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:06,790
"When Captain Ye was killed,

555
00:26:06,790 --> 00:26:07,920
this woman delivered food to me,

556
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:08,320
right?

557
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:09,500
Now both of them have disappeared—

558
00:26:09,500 --> 00:26:11,110
don't you find that suspicious?"

559
00:26:11,110 --> 00:26:12,000
Chief Qi, I've noticed

560
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:12,790
Chief Zhang

561
00:26:12,830 --> 00:26:14,230
is extremely observant.

562
00:26:16,070 --> 00:26:17,200
"Someone's been here."

563
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:18,200
And when Li Feng

564
00:26:18,200 --> 00:26:20,000
admitted he was a wanted criminal,

565
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:23,000
Chief Zhang was the only one
who remained completely calm.

566
00:26:23,000 --> 00:26:24,300
That's not right.

567
00:26:25,590 --> 00:26:26,440
That's not right at all.

568
00:26:26,440 --> 00:26:26,830
If...

569
00:26:27,330 --> 00:26:29,180
If he's really that capable,

570
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:30,110
why does he

571
00:26:30,110 --> 00:26:30,960
stay behind the scenes

572
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:32,400
and let you
and Song Xing do the work?

573
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:34,120
Chief Zhang used to be

574
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:36,590
a disciple of Director Gao,
when he was at the Provincial Department.

575
00:26:36,590 --> 00:26:38,240
From the Fengqi Road serial murders

576
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:39,240
to the White Elephant case—

577
00:26:39,240 --> 00:26:40,840
he's handled 17 major cases.

578
00:26:41,310 --> 00:26:42,640
So this time...

579
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:43,980
What?

580
00:26:46,110 --> 00:26:47,590
He didn't want to take the spotlight.

581
00:26:47,590 --> 00:26:49,120
Didn't want the spotlight?

582
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:50,960
Well, that means

583
00:26:50,960 --> 00:26:52,240
he couldn't afford to take it.

584
00:26:52,240 --> 00:26:53,300
But why?

585
00:26:54,510 --> 00:26:55,550
I can answer that.

586
00:26:56,460 --> 00:26:57,750
I just called Yan

587
00:26:57,750 --> 00:26:59,410
at the Provincial Department

588
00:26:59,830 --> 00:27:01,290
to ask about Zhang Yi'ang.

589
00:27:02,000 --> 00:27:02,720
Do you know

590
00:27:02,750 --> 00:27:04,340
why he left the bureau back then?

591
00:27:04,340 --> 00:27:05,100
I heard

592
00:27:05,160 --> 00:27:05,620
it was

593
00:27:05,720 --> 00:27:07,140
during a suspect chase.

594
00:27:07,590 --> 00:27:08,640
He tried to talk the suspect down,

595
00:27:08,640 --> 00:27:10,110
but the man ended up
falling to his death.

596
00:27:10,110 --> 00:27:11,710
There's another version...

597
00:27:13,030 --> 00:27:13,640
-Calm down!
-Back up!

598
00:27:13,640 --> 00:27:14,920
I said put the knife down!

599
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:15,750
Back off! Back off!

600
00:27:15,750 --> 00:27:16,440
-Calm down.
-Calm down.

601
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:16,830
Don't move!

602
00:27:16,830 --> 00:27:17,310
Calm down!

603
00:27:17,310 --> 00:27:18,240
Don't come any closer!

604
00:27:18,240 --> 00:27:19,440
-Calm down!
-Don't come over!

605
00:27:19,440 --> 00:27:20,500
Put the knife down!

606
00:27:20,590 --> 00:27:21,200
Quiet!

607
00:27:22,350 --> 00:27:24,410
Don't provoke him—I'll handle this.

608
00:27:29,440 --> 00:27:31,240
Shi Ge is trying to talk you down,

609
00:27:31,350 --> 00:27:32,720
Yu is trying to talk you down,

610
00:27:32,720 --> 00:27:33,640
and I definitely am too...

611
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:35,440
I don't need you talking me down.

612
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:37,400
Why are you so talkative?

613
00:27:38,790 --> 00:27:39,550
If those two pieces of lips

614
00:27:39,550 --> 00:27:40,880
on your face move again,

615
00:27:41,590 --> 00:27:42,480
I'll jump right now.

616
00:27:42,480 --> 00:27:43,680
Dying is easy.

617
00:27:44,080 --> 00:27:45,350
I-It doesn't take much resolve.

618
00:27:45,350 --> 00:27:45,960
Take us two

619
00:27:45,960 --> 00:27:47,310
right now—

620
00:27:47,310 --> 00:27:48,970
if I accidentally push you...

621
00:27:57,720 --> 00:27:59,480
The truth about what happened back then—

622
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:01,480
only the officers on the scene knew.

623
00:28:01,790 --> 00:28:03,010
But afterward,

624
00:28:03,400 --> 00:28:05,130
no one ever mentioned it again.

625
00:28:05,680 --> 00:28:06,590
Anyway, Zhang Yi'ang

626
00:28:06,590 --> 00:28:08,200
was eventually transferred out of CID

627
00:28:08,200 --> 00:28:10,240
and sent to the Veteran Cadre Bureau.

628
00:28:10,240 --> 00:28:11,920
So he became disillusioned

629
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:13,200
with criminal investigation, huh?

630
00:28:13,200 --> 00:28:14,240
Even if he discovered leads

631
00:28:14,240 --> 00:28:15,480
that we couldn't,

632
00:28:15,590 --> 00:28:16,640
he still wouldn't step forward.

633
00:28:16,640 --> 00:28:17,240
Exactly.

634
00:28:17,750 --> 00:28:18,720
And on top of that,

635
00:28:18,720 --> 00:28:21,450
there were people
giving him attitude every day.

636
00:28:24,510 --> 00:28:25,910
Chief Zhang can't leave.

637
00:28:26,200 --> 00:28:27,700
But his leg is injured

638
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:29,680
and he needs to go back
to the provincial capital for treatment—

639
00:28:29,680 --> 00:28:30,550
what reason do we have

640
00:28:30,550 --> 00:28:31,270
to stop him?

641
00:28:31,550 --> 00:28:33,750
We'll find any reason we can,
but he has to stay.

642
00:28:33,750 --> 00:28:34,370
How?

643
00:28:35,310 --> 00:28:36,590
Alright, it's fine.

644
00:28:36,720 --> 00:28:37,450
Don't worry.

645
00:28:37,590 --> 00:28:38,510
I'll reach out once I get there.

646
00:28:38,510 --> 00:28:39,040
Alright.

647
00:28:39,070 --> 00:28:39,670
Take care.

648
00:28:41,520 --> 00:28:43,410
[Police]

649
00:28:45,550 --> 00:28:46,480
Where's Li Qian?

650
00:28:46,750 --> 00:28:47,510
I'll go call her.

651
00:28:47,510 --> 00:28:48,110
No need, no need.

652
00:28:48,110 --> 00:28:49,000
Let her keep working.

653
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:49,720
You all go ahead and do your jobs.

654
00:28:49,720 --> 00:28:50,920
That's totally fine.

655
00:28:51,750 --> 00:28:52,570
Yi'ang,

656
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:54,030
time was too tight this time.

657
00:28:54,030 --> 00:28:55,160
We should've held

658
00:28:55,200 --> 00:28:56,200
a proper farewell ceremony for you.

659
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:56,680
No need.

660
00:28:58,030 --> 00:28:58,560
Chief Qi,

661
00:28:59,240 --> 00:29:00,040
Captain Wang,

662
00:29:00,480 --> 00:29:01,550
although we haven't known each other

663
00:29:01,550 --> 00:29:02,360
for long,

664
00:29:02,880 --> 00:29:03,410
I already

665
00:29:03,720 --> 00:29:05,620
feel a deep trust

666
00:29:05,750 --> 00:29:07,260
and bond

667
00:29:07,290 --> 00:29:08,420
with everyone here.

668
00:29:11,350 --> 00:29:12,750
I'd like to recite a poem.

669
00:29:14,200 --> 00:29:14,730
Go ahead.

670
00:29:15,110 --> 00:29:15,920
We'll all

671
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:17,000
remember it.

672
00:29:19,380 --> 00:29:20,730
"If life deceives you,

673
00:29:21,880 --> 00:29:23,010
do not be distressed

674
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:24,240
or anxious.

675
00:29:26,000 --> 00:29:27,060
In sorrowful days,

676
00:29:27,340 --> 00:29:28,180
remain calm;

677
00:29:29,510 --> 00:29:31,440
joyful days will surely come."

678
00:29:32,070 --> 00:29:33,380
Chief Zhang!

679
00:29:41,770 --> 00:29:43,030
Wait—what's going on?

680
00:29:43,920 --> 00:29:44,960
You're leaving too?

681
00:29:44,960 --> 00:29:45,590
Chief Qi,

682
00:29:46,510 --> 00:29:47,350
I really can't stay

683
00:29:47,350 --> 00:29:48,350
in Sanjiangkou anymore.

684
00:29:48,350 --> 00:29:48,790
Wait.

685
00:29:49,350 --> 00:29:50,160
What are you talking about?

686
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:51,350
How does this have to do with you?

687
00:29:51,350 --> 00:29:52,070
It does.

688
00:29:52,550 --> 00:29:53,440
Actually,

689
00:29:54,270 --> 00:29:55,640
Chief Zhang's second injury

690
00:29:55,640 --> 00:29:56,800
was caused by me.

691
00:29:57,350 --> 00:29:59,810
I'm consumed with guilt
and self-reproach.

692
00:30:00,030 --> 00:30:01,160
It was my own fault.

693
00:30:01,270 --> 00:30:02,130
I was careless.

694
00:30:02,160 --> 00:30:03,820
I can't forgive myself for it.

695
00:30:03,960 --> 00:30:05,440
So I've decided—I'm going back

696
00:30:05,440 --> 00:30:08,100
to the Provincial Department
with Chief Zhang.

697
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:10,510
I will personally report my mistake
to Director Gao.

698
00:30:10,510 --> 00:30:11,030
No need.

699
00:30:11,190 --> 00:30:11,720
I insist!

700
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:13,160
Wherever you go, I go.

701
00:30:13,270 --> 00:30:14,330
If you stay, I stay.

702
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:17,790
I should take responsibility
for taking care of you until you recover.

703
00:30:17,790 --> 00:30:18,640
You stay in Sanjiangkou

704
00:30:18,640 --> 00:30:19,350
and focus on improving yourself.

705
00:30:19,350 --> 00:30:21,480
Trust me—this is a great opportunity.

706
00:30:23,750 --> 00:30:24,480
Come back...

707
00:30:24,830 --> 00:30:25,350
Chief Zhang,

708
00:30:25,350 --> 00:30:26,480
why are you so stubborn?

709
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:27,750
You're not going anywhere.

710
00:30:27,750 --> 00:30:28,690
What's going on...

711
00:30:28,690 --> 00:30:29,820
We know everything.

712
00:30:32,110 --> 00:30:32,750
Know what?

713
00:30:34,030 --> 00:30:34,830
Catching Li Feng—

714
00:30:34,830 --> 00:30:36,630
you planned that from the start.

715
00:30:36,720 --> 00:30:38,160
The citywide DUI crackdown

716
00:30:38,160 --> 00:30:39,000
wasn't a bad call.

717
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:40,260
It was a masterstroke.

718
00:30:40,440 --> 00:30:41,110
You'd already spotted the flaws

719
00:30:41,110 --> 00:30:42,380
in Chief Lu's case,

720
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:43,040
right?

721
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:45,720
You're always one step ahead of us,

722
00:30:45,720 --> 00:30:46,920
but you won't tell us—

723
00:30:46,920 --> 00:30:47,730
am I right?

724
00:30:48,110 --> 00:30:48,720
Yi'ang,

725
00:30:49,310 --> 00:30:50,240
just admit it.

726
00:30:51,440 --> 00:30:52,240
Admit what?

727
00:30:52,640 --> 00:30:53,200
Admit that you

728
00:30:53,200 --> 00:30:54,160
arranged all of this.

729
00:30:54,160 --> 00:30:54,590
Chief.

730
00:30:56,590 --> 00:30:57,850
I'm a straight talker.

731
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:59,000
I'm a straight talker.

732
00:30:59,000 --> 00:31:00,260
I say things straight.

733
00:31:00,750 --> 00:31:01,460
I know

734
00:31:01,480 --> 00:31:03,680
you've got your reasons for doing this,

735
00:31:04,070 --> 00:31:05,830
but Ye Jian was like
a big brother to me.

736
00:31:05,830 --> 00:31:07,160
Anyone who'd dare
touch him in Sanjiangkou

737
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:08,150
isn't ordinary.

738
00:31:08,550 --> 00:31:09,870
I know my limits.

739
00:31:10,030 --> 00:31:12,290
If we want to crack this case,
we need you.

740
00:31:12,350 --> 00:31:13,210
I'm asking you—

741
00:31:13,440 --> 00:31:14,170
please stay.

742
00:31:15,070 --> 00:31:15,550
Yi'ang,

743
00:31:16,230 --> 00:31:17,160
logically speaking,

744
00:31:17,160 --> 00:31:18,070
you're injured,

745
00:31:18,070 --> 00:31:20,410
and we should respect your decision,

746
00:31:20,590 --> 00:31:21,030
right?

747
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:23,670
But the whole department needs you.

748
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:24,720
We all need you.

749
00:31:25,160 --> 00:31:25,770
Stay.

750
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:26,840
Please stay.

751
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:27,730
Chief Zhang,

752
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:29,680
we truly need your experience,

753
00:31:29,680 --> 00:31:30,790
your judgment, and your methods here.

754
00:31:30,790 --> 00:31:31,520
She's right—

755
00:31:31,830 --> 00:31:33,540
we mainly need your mind.

756
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:34,440
How about this:

757
00:31:34,440 --> 00:31:35,270
you stay,

758
00:31:35,310 --> 00:31:36,200
and I'll find you a hospital

759
00:31:36,200 --> 00:31:36,960
to treat your leg,

760
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:37,490
alright?

761
00:31:37,510 --> 00:31:38,630
You can command from behind the scenes.

762
00:31:38,630 --> 00:31:39,510
What do you think?

763
00:31:39,510 --> 00:31:40,440
Let me be your left hand.

764
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:41,310
Let me be your right hand.

765
00:31:41,310 --> 00:31:42,200
Let me be your legs.

766
00:31:42,200 --> 00:31:43,070
I, uh...

767
00:31:43,070 --> 00:31:44,480
We've run out of body parts, Chief.

768
00:31:44,480 --> 00:31:45,960
I'll call Director Gao

769
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:46,960
and get his approval right now—

770
00:31:46,960 --> 00:31:47,400
okay?

771
00:31:47,750 --> 00:31:49,010
That's not necessary.

772
00:31:49,750 --> 00:31:50,480
Chief Zhang—

773
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:51,720
your legs are better?

774
00:31:51,720 --> 00:31:52,590
So you're staying?

775
00:31:52,590 --> 00:31:54,510
What's the spirit of the police force?

776
00:31:54,510 --> 00:31:55,780
What's a key officer?

777
00:31:56,550 --> 00:31:57,720
This is exactly the kind of talent

778
00:31:57,720 --> 00:31:59,000
our bureau needs.

779
00:31:59,400 --> 00:32:00,600
You're right, Chief.

780
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:05,720
"A master detective"?

781
00:32:05,720 --> 00:32:06,450
Chief Zhang,

782
00:32:06,880 --> 00:32:09,160
Sanjiangkou really can't do without you.

783
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:09,960
With you here,

784
00:32:10,920 --> 00:32:13,380
we'll surely clear the fog
and see the truth.

785
00:32:18,590 --> 00:32:19,590
Looks like

786
00:32:20,160 --> 00:32:22,360
I'm not leaving Sanjiangkou after all.

787
00:32:41,800 --> 00:32:42,700
[Sanjiangkou Master Detective:
Cunning Schemes to Crack the Mystery Case]

788
00:32:42,870 --> 00:32:43,700
[New Deputy Police Chief Zhang Yiang
Captures Serial Killer]

789
00:32:46,160 --> 00:32:47,510
Fifteen murders...

790
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:50,060
how many death sentences is that?

791
00:32:50,480 --> 00:32:52,080
Let's not discuss work here.

792
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:56,550
Isn't that the guy
from the elevator the other day?

793
00:32:56,550 --> 00:32:57,610
He is Zhang Yi'ang?

794
00:33:00,750 --> 00:33:01,720
He's only been here a few days

795
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:02,880
and already caught a killer

796
00:33:02,880 --> 00:33:04,080
with 15 bodies on him.

797
00:33:04,880 --> 00:33:06,080
Pretty capable, huh.

798
00:33:06,160 --> 00:33:09,220
Li Feng, an A-level wanted suspect,
has been arrested.

799
00:33:13,130 --> 00:33:14,200
Didn't you say Fei brought

800
00:33:14,200 --> 00:33:15,350
in a heavy hitter?
What was his name?

801
00:33:15,350 --> 00:33:16,000
Li Feng.

802
00:33:20,830 --> 00:33:22,630
Zhang Yi'ang's got some skills.

803
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:24,960
I'd like to meet him.

804
00:33:26,720 --> 00:33:28,030
Meeting a cop—

805
00:33:28,160 --> 00:33:30,270
won't that be a bit too high-profile?

806
00:33:30,790 --> 00:33:31,720
If he's capable of getting to the truth

807
00:33:31,720 --> 00:33:32,550
behind Ye's death,

808
00:33:32,550 --> 00:33:34,000
then of course I want to meet him.

809
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:35,310
If he's not,

810
00:33:35,510 --> 00:33:36,310
there's no need for us

811
00:33:36,310 --> 00:33:37,170
to keep hiding.

812
00:33:38,590 --> 00:33:40,990
Mr. Rong, good thing
you had the foresight.

813
00:33:41,880 --> 00:33:43,340
Fei's line is already cut—

814
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:45,560
no one can trace it back to us.

815
00:33:46,440 --> 00:33:47,590
What about Li Penggai?

816
00:33:47,590 --> 00:33:50,510
You could give him ten lives
and he still wouldn't try it.

817
00:33:50,510 --> 00:33:52,970
Tell him not to show up
at the company for now.

818
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:54,730
Jianren,

819
00:33:55,880 --> 00:33:57,410
he's been with us for years—

820
00:33:57,720 --> 00:33:59,160
don't let him feel slighted,

821
00:33:59,160 --> 00:34:00,920
and don't give anyone reason
to get suspicious.

822
00:34:00,920 --> 00:34:02,180
Don't worry, Mr. Rong.

823
00:34:13,510 --> 00:34:14,320
That's the situation

824
00:34:14,320 --> 00:34:15,440
at the moment.

825
00:34:18,110 --> 00:34:18,840
But Jianren,

826
00:34:19,760 --> 00:34:20,360
why?

827
00:34:21,480 --> 00:34:22,510
The cops chased me

828
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:23,840
like I was a dog

829
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:27,710
when I was handling the task
for the company.

830
00:34:27,710 --> 00:34:30,840
Even if I didn't get results,
at least I put in the effort.

831
00:34:32,770 --> 00:34:33,429
Jianren...

832
00:34:34,510 --> 00:34:35,070
wait,

833
00:34:36,230 --> 00:34:38,090
this isn't a send-off meal, is it?

834
00:34:41,880 --> 00:34:42,679
Step outside.

835
00:34:55,360 --> 00:34:56,290
What do you know?

836
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:59,490
The company's planning
to put you to good use.

837
00:35:00,110 --> 00:35:01,110
Put me to good use?

838
00:35:01,440 --> 00:35:02,030
Then why are you sending me

839
00:35:02,030 --> 00:35:04,030
to a construction site to haul sand?

840
00:35:04,190 --> 00:35:04,930
Jianren,

841
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:06,400
I didn't get much schooling—

842
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:07,800
just be straight with me.

843
00:35:08,110 --> 00:35:08,960
If I've done anything wrong, I'll fix it.

844
00:35:08,960 --> 00:35:09,440
I, Li Penggai,

845
00:35:09,440 --> 00:35:10,840
I-I can change anything.

846
00:35:12,050 --> 00:35:13,240
I swear...

847
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:15,550
You know how big companies

848
00:35:15,550 --> 00:35:16,410
and corporates

849
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:17,960
train people these days?

850
00:35:19,320 --> 00:35:21,000
You start at the bottom.

851
00:35:21,630 --> 00:35:23,240
Work your way up.

852
00:35:24,150 --> 00:35:24,680
Way up...

853
00:35:28,190 --> 00:35:30,510
When heaven is about to entrust someone
with great responsibility,

854
00:35:30,510 --> 00:35:32,190
it first brings suffering to...

855
00:35:32,190 --> 00:35:32,590
and labor to...

856
00:35:32,590 --> 00:35:33,630
Anyway, that's the idea.

857
00:35:33,630 --> 00:35:34,230
You get it?

858
00:35:35,030 --> 00:35:35,920
This is Mr. Rong

859
00:35:35,920 --> 00:35:37,380
looking out for you.

860
00:35:37,590 --> 00:35:39,650
Short-term pain for long-term gain.

861
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:42,860
So, Jianren...

862
00:35:42,880 --> 00:35:43,190
Jianren.

863
00:35:43,190 --> 00:35:45,250
It's not that I lack confidence,

864
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:46,550
I just want to ask—

865
00:35:46,920 --> 00:35:49,110
Rongcheng Group's full
of talented people,

866
00:35:49,110 --> 00:35:51,640
so why am I the one
getting this "honor" first?

867
00:35:53,230 --> 00:35:53,760
Exactly—

868
00:35:56,030 --> 00:35:56,920
think about it.

869
00:35:58,230 --> 00:35:59,560
Yeah, think it through.

870
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:01,400
You need to use your head.

871
00:36:04,960 --> 00:36:05,660
You want me to...

872
00:36:05,660 --> 00:36:06,660
to... go to

873
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:08,170
a construction site...

874
00:36:09,670 --> 00:36:10,380
I can...

875
00:36:13,710 --> 00:36:15,370
Jianren, I've figured it out—

876
00:36:16,000 --> 00:36:16,800
you mean

877
00:36:17,630 --> 00:36:19,160
grooming me as a successor?

878
00:36:20,150 --> 00:36:21,150
Mr. Rong wants

879
00:36:21,230 --> 00:36:22,840
to train me to take over—

880
00:36:33,280 --> 00:36:35,880
Ye's memorial is tomorrow?

881
00:36:36,920 --> 00:36:38,550
That's what the notice says.

882
00:36:41,190 --> 00:36:42,120
Spread the word—

883
00:36:42,230 --> 00:36:43,830
have the guys all
go see Ye off

884
00:36:44,150 --> 00:36:45,230
one last time.

885
00:36:55,430 --> 00:37:03,290
[In Deepest Mourning of Comrade Ye Jian]

886
00:37:15,440 --> 00:37:19,010
[In Deepest Mourning of Comrade Ye Jian]

887
00:37:39,430 --> 00:37:44,940
[In Deepest Mourning of Comrade Ye Jian]

888
00:37:48,630 --> 00:37:49,480
Make sure the family
is fully taken care of.

889
00:37:49,480 --> 00:37:49,940
Yes, Sir.

890
00:37:49,940 --> 00:37:50,480
Right?

891
00:37:50,920 --> 00:37:51,670
You two...

892
00:37:51,760 --> 00:37:52,490
Understood.

893
00:38:10,630 --> 00:38:11,360
Who are they?

894
00:38:11,920 --> 00:38:13,480
The one in the middle—the tallest—

895
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:14,210
is Zhou Rong,

896
00:38:14,960 --> 00:38:15,670
a real estate developer,

897
00:38:15,670 --> 00:38:17,270
the boss of Rongcheng Group.

898
00:38:17,480 --> 00:38:18,630
The one on the left with glasses

899
00:38:18,630 --> 00:38:19,400
is Hu Jianren,

900
00:38:19,400 --> 00:38:20,190
his right-hand man,

901
00:38:20,190 --> 00:38:21,800
executive assistant at Rongcheng Group.

902
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:23,510
The one on the right,
with long hair and a beard—

903
00:38:23,510 --> 00:38:24,800
the one who looks shady—

904
00:38:24,800 --> 00:38:25,860
that's Lang Bowen.

905
00:38:26,150 --> 00:38:26,760
And the one behind them,

906
00:38:26,760 --> 00:38:27,880
a bit shorter,

907
00:38:27,880 --> 00:38:29,000
is Lu Yibo,

908
00:38:29,400 --> 00:38:31,110
manager of the Fenglinwan Hotel—

909
00:38:31,110 --> 00:38:33,040
the biggest hotel in Sanjiangkou.

910
00:38:56,070 --> 00:38:57,400
What does Lang Bowen do?

911
00:38:58,070 --> 00:38:59,370
He owns Aotu Company—

912
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:01,550
he works with Zhou Rong in real estate.

913
00:39:01,550 --> 00:39:02,800
Zhou Rong handles land acquisition;

914
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:04,400
he handles demolition and construction.

915
00:39:04,400 --> 00:39:05,150
The two companies

916
00:39:05,150 --> 00:39:07,630
operate upstream
and downstream of each other.

917
00:39:07,630 --> 00:39:09,190
And that kid is Lang Botu,

918
00:39:09,440 --> 00:39:11,170
Lang Bowen's younger brother.

919
00:39:19,110 --> 00:39:21,910
How... how come he doesn't
even look like himself?

920
00:39:23,030 --> 00:39:23,510
Get up.

921
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:30,630
Why would Ye

922
00:39:30,630 --> 00:39:31,830
be mixed up with them?

923
00:39:31,920 --> 00:39:33,180
They grew up together—

924
00:39:33,190 --> 00:39:34,390
hang out all the time.

925
00:39:34,920 --> 00:39:37,150
Normally, Ye should've kept his distance

926
00:39:37,150 --> 00:39:38,280
to avoid suspicion,

927
00:39:38,710 --> 00:39:39,590
but he never

928
00:39:39,590 --> 00:39:40,710
bothered.

929
00:39:42,190 --> 00:39:44,630
He's gone cold...

930
00:39:45,190 --> 00:39:46,310
Ye Jian!

931
00:39:46,340 --> 00:39:48,550
Wake up! Ye Jian!

932
00:39:48,710 --> 00:39:50,070
Why are you so cold?

933
00:39:51,070 --> 00:39:52,640
Chief Lu had it looked into before,

934
00:39:52,640 --> 00:39:54,100
but after digging into it,

935
00:39:54,190 --> 00:39:55,480
they found no business dealings

936
00:39:55,480 --> 00:39:56,610
between Ye and them.

937
00:39:57,230 --> 00:39:58,510
Financially, everything was clean—

938
00:39:58,510 --> 00:39:59,840
they were just friends.

939
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:02,650
Call him! Cakk him now!

940
00:40:02,960 --> 00:40:04,030
Call him!

941
00:40:04,030 --> 00:40:06,840
Wake him up—call him!

942
00:40:07,670 --> 00:40:09,700
Don't drag me—

943
00:40:09,840 --> 00:40:11,030
call him!

944
00:40:11,030 --> 00:40:12,110
Ye knew what he was doing.

945
00:40:12,110 --> 00:40:13,630
Call him! Call him!

946
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:15,800
You call him! Jian!

947
00:40:16,230 --> 00:40:18,090
Jian! Jian!

948
00:40:31,510 --> 00:40:32,240
Chief Zhang.

949
00:40:32,710 --> 00:40:33,190
Hello.

950
00:40:38,110 --> 00:40:39,160
This is my card—

951
00:40:39,550 --> 00:40:40,150
Zhou Rong.

952
00:40:41,590 --> 00:40:41,950
[Zhou Rong, Chairman]

953
00:40:42,390 --> 00:40:42,770
[Rongcheng]

954
00:40:42,800 --> 00:40:43,800
I saw the report

955
00:40:44,230 --> 00:40:45,280
about you catching a fugitive

956
00:40:45,280 --> 00:40:46,800
with 15 murders on him.

957
00:40:47,670 --> 00:40:49,320
They're calling you a master detective.

958
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:51,450
I'm counting on you for Ye Jian's case—

959
00:40:52,230 --> 00:40:52,960
please,

960
00:40:53,760 --> 00:40:55,760
whatever it takes, find the killer.

961
00:40:55,800 --> 00:40:57,460
If you need anything, call me—

962
00:40:58,110 --> 00:40:58,970
anytime, 24/7.

963
00:40:59,190 --> 00:40:59,720
Alright.

964
00:41:00,480 --> 00:41:01,070
I can see

965
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:02,070
you mean it.

966
00:41:03,590 --> 00:41:04,510
Catching the killer—

967
00:41:04,510 --> 00:41:05,670
that's our job,

968
00:41:06,670 --> 00:41:07,630
no matter who the victim was.
